#: src/pages/docs/ContainerPage.tsx:175
msgid "When the config has a <0>[control]</0> section, the binary binds that listener and serves the web UI, REST API, and docs alongside the engine. Authenticate callers with a bearer token — supply it through the <1>MULTIVIEW_CONTROL_TOKEN</1> environment variable so it is never baked into an image or written to the config file. The presented token is <2>admin.<secret></2>; if the variable is unset, the server generates one and logs it once at startup. Publish the listener's port (default <3>8080</3>) to reach it."
msgstr "When the config has a <0>[control]</0> section, the binary binds that listener and serves the web UI, REST API, and docs alongside the engine. Authenticate callers with a bearer token — supply it through the <1>MULTIVIEW_CONTROL_TOKEN</1> environment variable so it is never baked into an image or written to the config file. The presented token is <2>admin.<secret></2>; if the variable is unset, the server generates one and logs it once at startup. Publish the listener's port (default <3>8080</3>) to reach it."

